"ARKS GP 2013 Preliminaries":
"We hereby announce the quest that will be used on the ARKS Grand Pris 2013 Preliminaries.
Please use it to practice for the preliminaries.

[Warning] This quest is for practice, and does not offer items or experience.
Please keep that in mind. For details and regulations, please see the official site."
